[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0456","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0456.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0270","title":"SGI IRIX Performer API Search Tool 目录遍历漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 操作系统自带的 Performer API Search Tool 中的 pfdispaly.cgi 脚本存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向 CGI 程序发送包含特殊路径序列（如 ../）的恶意 HTTP 请求，突破 Web 根目录限制，读取服务器上任意文件，包括 /etc/passwd 等敏感系统文件。该漏洞影响安装了 performer_tools 组件的 SGI IRIX 系统，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。厂商已发布安全公告建议禁用相关 CGI 脚本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0270"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-04-03T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:02.600","remediation":"建议立即升级 SGI Performer API Search Tool 至最新补丁版本，或从 Web 服务器中移除 pfdispaly.cgi 脚本。如无法升级，可在 Web 服务器配置中限制对 pfdispaly.cgi 的访问（如禁用该 CGI 执行权限、限制访问来源 IP），并部署 Web 应用防火墙拦截目录遍历攻击载荷。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/i-041.shtml","http://www.osvdb.org/134","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/64","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/810","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0270.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0270.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0270","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0270.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0270.json","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/2d2ea2d13a3a7facfa195486d4f9782c62a06518/1999/CVE-1999-0270.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/1b69cf2313f68e29acceed58f52f6109cd37bb04/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-02xx/CVE-1999-0270.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0270.json","https://github.com/CyberSecAI/cve_info/blob/03b7e36424574a3a9ba5fd13480a326b666a1046/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0270.json","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelist-dev/blob/5b8fbb570438e8094550205589cc6f1d122acc94/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0270.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0456.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1381","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1381.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1183","title":"SGI IRIX System Manager sysmgr 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 6.4 和 6.3 的 System Manager (sysmgr) 图形界面存在远程命令执行漏洞。攻击者可构造恶意的 runtask 或 runexec 描述文件，当用户 Mailcap 条目关联了 x-sgi-task 或 x-sgi-exec MIME 类型时，sysmgr 会执行该描述文件中指定的任意系统命令，导致攻击者以 sysmgr 权限远程执行任意命令。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1183"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1998-04-02","updated":"2024-11-20","remediation":"安装 SGI 安全公告 19980403-01-PX 和 19980403-02-PX 提供的补丁程序；编辑 Mailcap 配置文件删除 x-sgi-task 和 x-sgi-exec 类型处理器关联；在防火墙限制对 sysmgr 服务端口的外部访问；如不需要系统管理器远程管理功能，建议直接停止并禁用 sysmgr 服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/809.php","http://www.osvdb.org/8556"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1381.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0815","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0815.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0551","title":"HP OpenMail 任意命令执行漏洞","description":"HP OpenMail 邮件系统存在安全配置缺陷，由于对打印请求的访问控制权限设置不当，拥有本地访问权限的攻击者可通过发送恶意构造的打印请求绕过安全限制，在目标系统上以 OpenMail 服务进程权限执行任意系统命令。该漏洞影响 HP OpenMail 服务器，攻击者需具备本地用户权限，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0551"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:37.113","remediation":"限制 HP OpenMail 打印服务仅允许受信任用户提交打印请求，在 OpenMail 配置中禁用不必要的命令执行接口，并升级到厂商修复此问题的最新版本。同时在系统层面限制 OpenMail 运行账户的最小权限，防止恶意打印请求执行任意命令。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9804-078"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0815.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0804","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0804.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0537","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 及 Netscape Navigator 活动内容执行漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 或 Netscape Navigator 等 Web 浏览器的安全配置不当，允许执行 ActiveX、Java、JavaScript 等活动内容。攻击者可构造恶意网页诱导用户访问，触发恶意代码执行，影响未正确配置安全设置的 IE 或 Netscape 用户。攻击者仅需诱导受害者访问恶意页面即可触发代码执行，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0537"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:36.140","remediation":"禁用浏览器中的 ActiveX、Java Applet 和 JavaScript 执行权限，在 IE 安全选项中将\"运行 ActiveX 控件和插件\"设为\"禁用\"或\"提示\"， Netscape 中取消勾选\"启用 Java\"和\"启用 JavaScript\"，建议升级至现代浏览器（如 Chrome/Firefox/Edge 最新版）并启用站点隔离与脚本阻断扩展。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0537","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-0537.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/442e3d0f3c777e02c70fc200a453fe1f1f8a2431/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0537.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0537","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/19ba23eb6f8fe22cdd9a46164160f96a7cf3fffd/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0537.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0537.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/51a0e15452743e596ced46bb3f156961c52df5bb/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-h76m-f5xr-xcrv/GHSA-h76m-f5xr-xcrv.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0537.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86056/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0804.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0761","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0761.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0507","title":"开源路由器弱口令漏洞","description":"路由器、防火墙或其他网络设备上存在具有弱口令（可猜测密码）的账户，攻击者无需身份认证即可通过远程网络尝试常见或默认凭据登录设备。该漏洞影响各类使用弱密码或默认账户配置的网络设备，攻击条件为攻击者能够与目标设备建立网络连通并访问其管理或服务端口。利用方式为通过暴力破解或字典攻击猜测账户密码，成功登录后可获取设备控制权，进而篡改路由策略、绕过防火墙规则或作为内网跳板，造成严重的安全风险。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0507"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:32.553","remediation":"立即更换所有网络设备（路由器、防火墙等）上的默认/弱口令为强密码（至少12位，含大小写字母、数字和特殊字符），禁用默认管理账户（如admin/root），启用账户锁定策略（连续5次失败后锁定30分钟），并定期（每90天）更换口令。对于支持TACACS+/RADIUS的设备，建议启用集中认证。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0507","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-0507.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c271719fd48dcc28619dc324e441b822d7b4bace/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0507.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0507","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1e2d061a60b9c6823d20cc72e51f709fadad54d2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0507.json","https://github.com/DefectDojo/django-DefectDojo/blob/d9905eb7656178d3e59e0bf8f1d53a9ee9e50186/unittests/scans/openvas/many_vuln.xml","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0507.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0507.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83210/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/jbeasl7/openvas-feed-sync-local/blob/7c8dc35196ef4eb644a4c5a923e3428412a226aa/openvas-feeds/nvt-feed/pre2008/DDI_WhatsUp_Default.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0761.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0761.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0442","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0442.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0257","title":"Linux Kernel IP Fragmentation Nestea 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"CVE-1999-0257 即 Nestea 变种 Teardrop IP 碎片拒绝服务攻击，攻击者向目标系统发送精心构造的、偏移量重叠的畸形 IP 分片数据包，目标系统在重组这些分片时因算法缺陷导致内存计算错误，引发系统崩溃或重启。该漏洞无需认证即可远程利用，影响 Linux Kernel 2.6.20.1 及众多早期操作系统版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0257"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:00.990","remediation":"升级 Linux 内核至 2.6.20.1 以上版本（如 2.6.21+），该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。无法升级时，可在 iptables 中添加规则丢弃畸形 IP 分片包：iptables -A INPUT -f -m limit --limit 100/s --limit-burst 100 -j ACCEPT 或使用防火墙过滤分片重叠的恶意数据包作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0257","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0257.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0257","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0257.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0257.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0257.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5h5w-wrfr-qmhc/GHSA-5h5w-wrfr-qmhc.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/N/nestea.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0257.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0442.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0229","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0229.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0098","title":"Sendmail SMTP HELO 命令缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Sendmail SMTP 服务在处理 HELO 命令时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标服务器的 25 端口发送特制的 HELO 请求触发该漏洞，成功利用可导致任意代码执行或服务崩溃，攻击者借此可完全控制服务器或隐藏恶意活动痕迹。该漏洞影响多个版本的 Sendmail，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0098"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:34.903","remediation":"立即升级 Sendmail 至 8.9.0 或更高版本（该版本修复了 SMTP HELO 命令缓冲区溢出问题）。SLMail 用户应升级至 3.0 及以上版本，Mercury Mail Server 用户升级至最新版本。如无法立即升级，可在防火墙层面限制 SMTP（TCP 25）端口仅允许可信来源访问，同时在 Sendmail 配置中限制 HELO 命令输入长度作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0098"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0229.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0015","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0015.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0003","title":"Common Desktop Environment ToolTalk RPC 服务缓冲区溢出远程代码执行漏洞","description":"ToolTalk 数据库服务器（rpc.ttdbserverd）存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证，通过向目标系统发送特制请求即可触发缓冲区溢出，从而以 root 权限执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 Xi Graphics Maximum CDE 1.2.3、TriTeal TED CDE 4.3 及 Sun Solaris 2.5.1 等系统，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重，属于当年最具破坏力的远程代码执行漏洞之一。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0003"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:18.353","remediation":"立即禁用 rpc.ttdbserverd 服务（进程名：rpc.ttdbserverd），执行 /usr/bin/killall rpc.ttdbserverd 终止进程，并从 /etc/inetd.conf（或 /etc/xinetd.d/）中注释 rstatd/rusersd 相关行后重启 inetd。对于 SGI IRIX，应安装 SGI 安全公告 19981101-01 中提供的补丁。对于 Sun Solaris 系统，应用 Sun 提供的对应安全补丁（如 SunOS 5.5.1 相关补丁）。上述操作系统均已终止安全支持，强烈建议迁移至受支持的现代操作系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/122","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19102","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0003.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0003.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0003","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0003.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/572.txt","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0003.md","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/rpc.rules","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0003.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/8954696320cbff8f7d95f98854cf0e72222fc646/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-gxwg-52wj-vc7w/GHSA-gxwg-52wj-vc7w.json","https://github.com/FIRSTdotorg/Vuln4Cast/blob/c93910d268aa5b5d2260adb9b5d92094b2d06daf/YearlyVuln4Cast-V1.ipynb"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0015.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1222","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1222.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0960","title":"SGI IRIX 6.2 cdplayer 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 6.2 系统自带的 cdplayer 程序存在本地权限提升漏洞。该程序在处理命令行参数时未对目标路径进行充分校验，导致本地普通用户可通过指定特定的命令行选项，在任意目录位置（包括本无权写入的系统目录）创建目录。攻击前提是攻击者需拥有目标系统的本地登录权限并能执行 cdplayer 程序。攻击者利用该缺陷可操纵文件系统结构，为后续进一步的权限提升或破坏系统完整性创造条件，从而造成本地权限提升危害。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0960"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-03-20T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:24.730","remediation":"建议升级至 SGI 官方修复版本（IRIX 6.3 或更高版本），并应用 SGI 发布的针对 cdplayer 的安全补丁。作为临时缓解措施，可移除 /usr/sbin/cdplayer 的 setuid 位（执行 chmod u-s /usr/sbin/cdplayer），或限制该程序仅供受信任用户使用，以防止本地用户利用命令行选项在任意位置创建目录进行提权。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19262","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/184a5a0fb7dfcbb1c5bcfd5178078c78dc1e4738/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0960.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0960","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0960.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/95eeda559fd899397df50f658cf25cf01bb1e4ea/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0960.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/8b1565557a8e0fb04634f0989d7e7dd7febd4847/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-627f-8vjf-xp74/GHSA-627f-8vjf-xp74.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0960.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154000_154100.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--da01f6de-65ad-4c64-89cc-2cb6261446f7.json","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--da01f6de-65ad-4c64-89cc-2cb6261446f7.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1222.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1322","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1322.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1075","title":"IBM AIX 4.1.5 inetd ttdbserver 端口连接拒绝服务漏洞","description":"IBM AIX 4.1.5 的 inetd 服务在启动 ToolTalk（ttdbserver）时动态分配端口 N，但同时会错误地在端口 N-1 上监听而不将控制权交给 ttdbserver。远程攻击者可向端口 N-1 发送大量连接请求，由于 inetd 无法正常关闭这些连接，导致系统资源耗尽进而引发拒绝服务。此漏洞影响 IBM AIX 4.1.5 版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1075"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-03-18T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:40.153","remediation":"建议安装 IBM inetd 补丁 IX70400（文件集 bos.net.tcp.client 4.1.5.12）修复该问题。如无法立即更新，可停止并禁用 ttdbserver（ToolTalk）服务来消除攻击面：执行 `stopsrc -s ttdbserver` 并注释 `/etc/inittab` 中的 ttdbserver 启动项。此外，可在防火墙或路由器上限制对 AIX 主机高端口（≥1024）的外部访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=89025820612530&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1322.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0152","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0152.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0060","title":"Lucent Ascend 系列路由器 Discard Service 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Lucent Ascend MAX 5.0/Pipeline 6.0/TNT 1.0/2.0 路由器存在拒绝服务漏洞。攻击者无需身份认证，只需向目标路由器的 discard 端口（UDP 端口 9，被 Java Configurator 工具使用）发送特制的畸形数据包，即可触发该漏洞，导致路由器服务崩溃或无法正常响应，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Lucent Ascend MAX、Pipeline 及 TNT 系列路由器，需引起相关运维人员重视。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0060"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-03-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:29.030","remediation":"在受影响路由器上配置访问控制列表（ACL），禁止外部来源向 UDP 端口 9（Discard 端口）发送数据包；如无需 Java Configurator 功能，建议在系统配置中禁用 Discard 服务。鉴于 Ascend MAX/Pipeline/TNT 系列已停止技术支持且无官方补丁可用，建议迁移至受支持的现代路由器硬件以彻底消除风险。作为临时缓解措施，可在网络边界防火墙处过滤目标端口为 UDP 9 的入站流量。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ascend.com/2695.html","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19555","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0060.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0060","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0060.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0060.md","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/281.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0060.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5j44-w6q9-hxx4/GHSA-5j44-w6q9-hxx4.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/dos.rules","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/A/ascend_kill.nasl","https://github.com/magicsword-io/Magic-SigExplorer/blob/2c28b91b003429a144a687199ee99ebd26f1a343/Magic-SigExplorer/docs/cve_report.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0152.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1339","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1339.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1118","title":"Sun Solaris ndd 本地拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Solaris 2.6 系统中的 ndd 工具存在安全配置缺陷，本地攻击者可通过修改特定 TCP/IP 协议栈参数（如 TCP 窗口大小、重传超时等），导致系统网络协议栈行为异常，进而引发拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Solaris 2.6 版本，攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限，无需高权限即可触发。由于 ndd 工具未对参数修改操作进行充分的权限校验和范围限制，导致低权限用户可滥用该工具破坏网络功能。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1118"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-03-11T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:45.513","remediation":"升级到受支持的 Solaris 版本（如 Solaris 11）或迁移至其他受支持操作系统。如无法升级，通过 chmod 700 /usr/sbin/ndd 限制 ndd 命令仅允许 root 执行，并通过 RBAC 策略细化网络参数修改权限，同时启用审计日志监控 ndd 调用行为。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/165&type=0&nav=sec.sba","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/433","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/817","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/a662dc905cd549a2105daacbfce64cf01652761d/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1118.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1118","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1118.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/263f37bc67cd24fe03a39077d8b57f3001369a95/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1118.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/bf2339193e1c10dc2db330718adeb8cc8d88c4dd/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-65xg-v5wp-9qwj/GHSA-65xg-v5wp-9qwj.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1118.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154000_154100.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--ba73844d-26ab-45be-a3a4-932204272907.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/26d249099e240aac89bdddbef7937b266937e448/1999.tsv","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_dos.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1339.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1441","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1441.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1272","title":"SGI IRIX cdrom 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"IRIX 操作系统 CDROM 可靠性检测程序（cdrom）存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。由于程序在处理 CDROM 设备检测数据时未对输入长度进行充分校验，本地攻击者可通过向该程序提交特制的超长输入数据触发栈缓冲区溢出，从而覆盖函数返回地址或关键数据结构。成功利用该漏洞可导致权限提升，攻击者将获得 root 权限，进而完全控制目标系统。该漏洞影响 IRIX 多个版本，攻击者需具备本地系统访问权限方可利用此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1272"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:05.070","remediation":"立即安装 SGI 安全公告 19980301-01-PX 中提供的补丁程序，该补丁修复了 cdrom 程序中的缓冲区溢出漏洞。由于 SGI IRIX 已停止维护，建议将系统迁移至受支持的操作系统（如 Linux）以彻底消除风险。如无法立即迁移，可通过限制本地用户对 cdrom 程序的执行权限（chmod 750 /usr/sbin/cdrom）作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1635","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1272.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1272","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1272.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/9b79b5eac5a874eeb91f0d9e37084feed8b830f5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1272.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-cqf3-4mqj-g93x/GHSA-cqf3-4mqj-g93x.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83033/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1272.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--d88e047e-f36f-49bf-a27a-92bac54de998.json","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_gainpre.txt","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1441.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0752","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0752.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0502","title":"Unix SSH 默认空口令远程登录漏洞","description":"Unix 系统存在默认账户或空密码配置漏洞，当管理员未设置密码或密码为空时，攻击者可通过 SSH 服务使用常见默认用户名（如 root、admin）进行远程登录尝试。成功登录后可获系统完全控制权限，执行任意命令。该漏洞影响大量未正确配置账户安全的 Unix/Linux 系统，利用难度低、危害严重。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0502"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:31.960","remediation":"立即检查所有本地 Unix 系统账户，为每个账户设置强密码（至少 12 位，含大小写字母、数字及特殊字符）；删除或禁用无密码账户及默认测试账户；配置 `/etc/shadow` 确保密码哈希字段非空；启用 PAM 模块 `pam_pwquality.so` 强制密码复杂度策略，并在 SSH 配置中设置 `PermitEmptyPasswords no` 禁止空密码登录。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0502","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/41694","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-0502.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/122439703ba8729c2a612b649ea87112305b8e28/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0502.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0502","https://github.com/ARPSyndicate/suricata-vedas/blob/fe24794ad36564b5bbc7c69101525011387b8650/1999/CVE-1999-0502.rules","https://github.com/e-m-b-a/emba/blob/968abdc74763b43a3cdd216fbb1950cab484f982/config/msf_cve-db.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/bc69cd1e5221f68ef56bd10c5c61adf76a19f0fc/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0502.json","https://github.com/vulncheck-oss/0day.today.archive/blob/3664abdd71985a44aff3260896a8f36e2f4a9682/remote-exploits/20781.txt","https://github.com/gottburgm/Exploits/blob/fd340a05cbec416e89bfae898e27bf5fcb429101/MSFExploits/DELL/MSF/Idrac_infos.txt","https://github.com/DefectDojo/django-DefectDojo/blob/d9905eb7656178d3e59e0bf8f1d53a9ee9e50186/unittests/scans/openvas/many_vuln.xml","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/account_lp.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0752.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0545","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0545.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0330","title":"Linux bdash 游戏缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Linux bdash 游戏程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向游戏程序提交特制的输入数据触发缓冲区溢出，成功利用后可获取 root 权限，实现本地权限提升。该漏洞影响运行 bdash 游戏的 Linux 系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。攻击前提是攻击者拥有系统的本地账户访问权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0330"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:10.070","remediation":"立即移除 bdash 游戏的 setuid root 权限位（执行 chmod u-s /usr/games/bdash），或直接卸载 bsdgames 软件包以彻底消除提权风险。如确需保留该游戏，应升级至已修复缓冲区边界检查的修补版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602558319119&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0545.toml"}]